<p>Her artist statement from a different <a href="https://gagosian.com/artists/jennifer-guidi/">website</a>(her <a href="https://www.jenniferguidi.com/">website</a> didn‚Äôt have one):</p>

<p>‚ÄúJennifer Guidi creates paintings notable for their luminosity, texture, and sculptural presence. Her swirling, mandala-like compositions oscillate in color and texture, inspiring shifts in perceptual awareness to forge new sensory horizons. Each painting is methodically executed through a unique process‚Äîat once systematic and organic‚Äîwhich reflects the connection of her painting practice to strains of Minimalism that privilege attention to detail and repetition. Her sculptural markings evoke an intensely meditative sense of narrative and spiritual votive. Guidi‚Äôs richness of palette and trademark use of sand as a medium link her mode of abstraction to tactile experiences of the natural world, from light permeating the landscape at dawn to the hazy atmospheric conditions of the West Coast.‚Äù</p>
